data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated 4 sided brick home in the heart of sought after Gresham Park! This spacious 4BR/3BA ranch is located on a quiet lot in a high demand, No HOA community, close to local eats, parks and easy access to I-20 and I-285. Bright, open floor plan with hardwoods throughout, formal living room, separate dining area, granite counter tops and stainless appliances. Private master suite at the rear of the home with updated bathroom and large walk in closet. Three additional bedrooms feature plenty of space, natural light and walk in closets as well as 2 more full baths.  Large back deck that overlooks fenced yard perfect for entertaining. Lots of square footage offered for the price in this up and coming revitalized area. This property could also be an ideal investment with proven income potential. Home is sold AS-IS and priced below comps.
